Feature: logowanie do portalu edukacyjnego Coders Lab https://lms.coderslab.pl

Scenario: logging on to educational portal Coders Lab at "https://lms.coderslab.pl"
GIVEN: an open browser page with address "https://lms.coderslab.pl/login"
WHEN: entering existing user data in "E-mail:" and "Hasło" input boxes
AND: clicking on "ZALOGUJ" button
THEN: successfully being redirected to page address "https://lms.coderslab.pl/courses" with user's courses displayed


Feature: uruchomienie pierwszej prezentacji z preworku Java na kursie testera automatyzującego.

Scenario: starting the first Java prework presentation from Automation Tester course
GIVEN: being logged on as an existing user on the page "https://lms.coderslab.pl/login" with user's courses displayed
WHEN: clicking on box "Tester automatyzujący"
AND: being redirected to page "https://lms.coderslab.pl/course/ONL_TEA_W_21"
AND: clicking on "POKAŻ ROZDZIAŁY" button within "00 Prework" section (first section on the page)
AND: clicking on "Wstęp do kursu" box
THEN: successfully being redirected to a page with "Wstęp" presentation being showed